{"tid":442632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國誕生新喜劇新星成傳媒焦點 或超越戇豆先生地位","createTime":"2017-10-20T22:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T02:38:29.000Z","uid":41245,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef344ec1c5762de02fe6e6e1fc156476d29a37bd","tid":442632,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T22:51:58.000Z","msg":"文翠珊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.buzzfeed.com/buzzfeed-static/static/2017-10/20/6/asset/buzzfeed-prod-fastlane-02/sub-buzz-19366-1508494915-1.jpg?downsize=700:*&amp;output-format=auto&amp;output-quality=auto\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.buzzfeed.com%2Fbuzzfeed-static%2Fstatic%2F2017-10%2F20%2F6%2Fasset%2Fbuzzfeed-prod-fastlane-02%2Fsub-buzz-19366-1508494915-1.jpg%3Fdownsize%3D700%3A%2A%26output-format%3Dauto%26output-quality%3Dauto&h=bf1f72bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPeople are sharing a picture of a lonely-looking Theresa May at a summit in Brussels as an example of how isolated Britain is during Brexit negotiations.<br />\n<br />\nThe prime minister hoped to move talks on to discuss trade, but EU leaders said they were <span style=\"color: red;\">only willing to talk about it among themselves.</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTheresa May Was Pictured Sitting Alone At The EU Summit And Everyone Made The Same Joke<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.buzzfeed.com/matthewchampion/theresa-may-and-the-infinite-sadness?utm_term=.uykMYkDQ8#.oyl1Y62yJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeed.com%2Fmatthewchampion%2Ftheresa-may-and-the-infinite-sadness%3Futm_term%3D.uykMYkDQ8%23.oyl1Y62yJ&d=SqI5g1WaY6r%2Fyy9H4DuS9DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=fd68ae26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.buzzfeed.com/matthewchampion/theresa-may-and-the-infinite-sadness?utm_term=.uykMYkDQ8#.oyl1Y62yJ</a><br />\n<br />\nTheresa May Has 8 Weeks To Prevent The Brexit Talks Collapsing Without A Deal<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.buzzfeed.com/albertonardelli/theresa-may-has-8-weeks-to-prevent-the-brexit-talks?utm_term=.xmMjmW8JN#.duAogkRq0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeed.com%2Falbertonardelli%2Ftheresa-may-has-8-weeks-to-prevent-the-brexit-talks%3Futm_term%3D.xmMjmW8JN%23.duAogkRq0&d=SqI5g1WaY6r%2Fyy9H4DuS9DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=5d2793ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.buzzfeed.com/albertonardelli/theresa-may-has-8-weeks-to-prevent-the-brexit-talks?utm_term=.xmMjmW8JN#.duAogkRq0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DMkmF1RXkAEKdmN?format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDMkmF1RXkAEKdmN%3Fformat%3Djpg&h=ba78a513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DMkn3MxWkAAzC8K?format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDMkn3MxWkAAzC8K%3Fformat%3Djpg&h=905e8732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相關圖片：<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/3Z0XdseX163wQ/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3Z0XdseX163wQ%2Fgiphy.gif&h=0f3af290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文翠珊於2016年成為首相，其喜劇感成英國於脫歐後之具體化之表現。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/xUNd9QHZOSU7zyXnoI/200w.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia3.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FxUNd9QHZOSU7zyXnoI%2F200w.gif&h=3c58911f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文翠珊於上月經同為笑仗明星手中收到外相莊漢生的解顧通知。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/OXA8U3SCCVxUk/200w.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FOXA8U3SCCVxUk%2F200w.gif&h=1a4ecd54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其喜劇才華時常成傳媒焦點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/a292153333e1ac14e79043d70dc22b77/tenor.gif?itemid=8911817\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fa292153333e1ac14e79043d70dc22b77%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D8911817&h=ab0cdccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文翠珊於脫歐後提前大選，表示爭取選票為與歐盟談判之籌碼，亦表示其滅工黨之決心。於傳媒一至睇好之際，文翠珊表現出勝利者姿態，直言拒絕進行競選宣傳及出席辯論。結果文翠珊帶領之保守黨得票大減，回應傳媒亦表現得體，稱得到英國人之支持，其厚面皮之表現為英式幽默中重要特色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663f30b46e1c8d48aee6dac9cdad1de89f00a100","tid":442632,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T23:24:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e5abc789f60b203bad5a4214f75b8abe443d289","tid":442632,"uid":9348,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T23:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/3Z0XdseX163wQ/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3Z0XdseX163wQ%2Fgiphy.gif&h=0f3af290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5a90a4b92f5c2ae791dd95e9e3847fee7146e5","tid":442632,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T23:36:35.000Z","msg":"咁有娛樂感都叫唔識玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0462df84693655ece626fe2d1712462305666b7","tid":442632,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T23:45:45.000Z","msg":"仲有之前玩人浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ce006b0892face5d04c0339b3973f2c95bf52b","tid":442632,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:14:50.000Z","msg":"好慘😯"},{"pid":"bd69023184c5c250c54887583405697a96708798","tid":442632,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:22:36.000Z","msg